title: Johann Sebastian Bach - Magnificat
description:
The greatest classical recording I&#039;ve heard.

The Swiss Radio Chorus and Ensemble Vanitis conducted by Diego Fasolis.

Tracks 1-12 are Magnifact BWV243 in D Major

13-23 Cantata BWV 21 "Ich hatte viel Bekummernis" For 8 voices in double choir

Antonelo Balducci- Soprano, Ulrike Clausen - alto, FreidernLang - tenor, Fulvio Bettini - Baritone


24-26 Motet BWV 225 "Singet dem Herrn ein ein nueues Lied

Roberta Invernizzi - Soprano, Annemeike Cantor - alto, Gerhard - Nenneman - Tenor, Furio Zanasi - Baritone

Recorded Live in Chiesa di S. Francesco, Locarno Switzerland 9/5/94

75 minutes of pure bliss. Enjoy!!
